<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFHonneth1995"><a href="/wiki/Axel_Honneth" title="Axel Honneth">Honneth, Axel</a> (1995), "The Limits of Liberalism: On the Political-Ethical Discussion Concerning Communitarianism", in Honneth, Axel, <i>The Fragmented World of the Social</i>, Albany: State University of New York Press, pp.&#160;231–247, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/079142300X" class="internal">ISBN 0-7914-2300-X</a></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Limits+of+Liberalism%3A++On+the+Political-Ethical+Discussion+Concerning+Communitarianism&amp;rft.atitle=The+Fragmented+World+of+the+Social&amp;rft.aulast=Honneth&amp;rft.aufirst=Axel&amp;rft.au=Honneth%2C+Axel&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B231%E2%80%93247&amp;rft.place=Albany&amp;rft.pub=State+University+of+New+York+Press&amp;rft.isbn=0-7914-2300-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Democratic_socialism"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
